  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the way I met the writer and told my story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she wrote the story and made it to her show.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was that particular experience like for you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that was odd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, first I didn't want to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I am very happy I did, because-- excuse me-- because that way, many school children and grownups also, but mainly school children, can see what hatred really means and where that can go.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like in the show, the little girl is envying another girl, and because of that, they hate that person.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by the end, they came to my story, seeing that this hatred can grow in grownups so much that they really can hurt people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I am very happy that tape was made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like to let people know that we should work for peace and fight for peace, and peace will never be if we don't make it possible.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe there could be peace in the whole world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would like to give the message to stop hatred.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It doesn't matter [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] against whom the hatred goes-- against the Jews or against blacks or Orientals or whoever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hatred is hatred, and we have to stop it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not with guns, but education and understanding and patience, because you have to give a chance to a person to understand what really hatred means and does to everyone.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To my testimony?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One thing that I usually say is that Hitler hated the Jews and ordered the Jews to be shot, and then put gasoline over them and burned, or in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It doesn't matter where.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
